    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "I discovered that spring was the Lord Jesus Christ—"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "He died for me and He’s alive!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Of my sins I was forgiv’n,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "But much more He had in store—"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "His very own life to give!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Where then does He give life? Well the Bible tells:"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "In my spirit where Jesus dwells!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Raised from death, He became breath,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Water too, even true food—"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "He’s processed to live in me!"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "2"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Christ lives in me"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "As the Spirit reaching me!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "This my song, all day long:"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Life is flowing free!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "He’s flooding me"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "As a river ceaselessly!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "This my God, to me brought:"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The processed Trinity!"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "chorus"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "If you haven’t yet found what your heart’s looking for,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Come and listen to His own word:"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "“Whoso drinks shall by no means"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Ever thirst; in him will burst"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "A fountain of life divine!”"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Come, oh come see this man! Is He not the Christ?"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "He came that you would have His life!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Just believe, then you will see"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "He’s so real, living, and free—"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "A genuine prayer’s the way:"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
